				</span>
			</figure>
		</div>
		
		
		<div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
			<p class="show-text">
				Climate of Portugal in the North is cool and rainy to-cold and snowy in winters. The climate in the South is hot and dry with temperatures frequenting 40 degrees celsius (104 Fahrenheit) in summers.
			</p>
		</div>
		
		
		<div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
