		<div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
			<p class="show-text">
				FIESA festival in Pera, on the Algarve, held since 2003, is the largest sand sculpture event in the world. The exhibition displays 40,000 tons of sand, sculpted by sand artists from all over the world. Some structures reach 12 meters (39 feet) in height.
			</p>
		</div>
		
		
		
		<div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
